Interface AssertThatIterable<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the Element type of the Iterator
    All Superinterfaces:
    AssertThatObject<Iterable<T>>

    public interface AssertThatIterable<T>
extends AssertThatObject<Iterable<T>>
    DSL on assertion on iterable.

    This interface is returned by the various methods assertThatIterable exposed by TestSuite.
